      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 70.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 70.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吾言甚易知，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My words are very easy to know, and very easy to practise;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-070__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-070</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 70.2 - 老子 70.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 70.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>甚易行。天下莫能知，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>but there is no one in the world who is able to know and able to practise them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-070__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-070</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 70.4 - 老子 70.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 70.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>莫能行。言有宗，事有君。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is an originating and all-comprehending (principle) in my words, and an authoritative law for the things (which I enforce).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-070__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-070</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 70.7 - 老子 70.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 70.4 - 老子 70.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫唯無知，是以不我知。知我者希，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It is because they do not know these, that men do not know me. They who know me are few, and I am on that account (the more) to be prized.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-070__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-070</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 70.10 - 老子 70.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 70.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>則我者貴。是以聖人被褐懷玉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It is thus that the sage wears (a poor garb of) hair cloth, while he carries his (signet of) jade in his bosom.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
